posts.post_title: SOLD: T206 Cobb Red Portrait PSA 3
posts.post_content:
Centered extremely well; graded properly as a "3"
Old(ish) label but in the thicker newer style slab. (Likely graded in early 2015)
$7750

[IMG]https://scontent-dfw5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/248487128_10100373519716050_133521072266037602_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-5&_nc_sid=b9115d&_nc_ohc=A2inGBz0XnMAX_MmJDF&tn=RRef8nD7eT666BIA&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw5-2.xx&oh=2e5e0d2c57968e739d5a3c0389666813&oe=619BF012[/IMG][IMG]https://scontent-dfw5-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/248441001_10100373519676130_4331082848492666392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-5&_nc_sid=b9115d&_nc_ohc=NKesCO6zWlwAX_TwA1n&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw5-1.xx&oh=6930ce99bcde0ec0ebbb40625531fe05&oe=619E23D1[/IMG]

Great color and registration.  That’s a sharp card!

Also, I really wish PSA would tell you when a card was graded.
